166
00:11:36,759 --> 00:11:41,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">背负起来的责任 我从来不会放弃</font>

167
00:11:43,269 --> 00:11:46,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗 看来这样的生活还要持续一阵子</font>

168
00:11:47,369 --> 00:11:51,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 只有我们两人的生活</font>

169
00:11:54,399 --> 00:11:55,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么？</font>

170
00:11:55,389 --> 00:11:56,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没什么</font>

171
00:11:57,159 --> 00:11:59,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是觉得也太和平了</font>

172
00:12:04,109 --> 00:12:06,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">伤春悲秋起来了？</font>

173
00:12:06,449 --> 00:12:07,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">才没有呢</font>

174
00:12:11,129 --> 00:12:13,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 这什么啊！</font>

175
00:12:13,019 --> 00:12:14,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可恶 好苦</font>

176
00:12:14,989 --> 00:12:16,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是你干的吗！</font>

177
00:12:17,629 --> 00:12:19,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是果汁而已</font>

178
00:12:20,189 --> 00:12:24,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">今天是为我庆祝吧 要奉陪到底哦</font>

179
00:12:25,609 --> 00:12:27,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你要喝什么？</font>

180
00:12:28,069 --> 00:12:29,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我已经…</font>

181
00:12:30,699 --> 00:12:33,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是说好要补偿我吗？</font>

182
00:12:33,529 --> 00:12:37,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">补偿？是当初苹果派那事儿吗</font>

183
00:12:38,509 --> 00:12:39,429
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你会…</font>

184
00:12:41,269 --> 00:12:42,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">听从我的要求吧？</font>

185
00:12:45,419 --> 00:12:48,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能再喝一杯了哦</font>

186
00:12:48,759 --> 00:12:50,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 我答应你</font>

187
00:12:57,619 --> 00:13:02,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后呢 然后呢 当时我还很小哦</font>

188
00:13:02,179 --> 00:13:08,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不小心吃下了西瓜的种子 一直在担心它会在胃里发芽</font>

189
00:13:08,499 --> 00:13:13,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉你摇摇晃晃的 是因为我太累了吗</font>

190
00:13:14,119 --> 00:13:21,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一直答应「再喝最后一杯」 感觉好像答应了10次？</font>

191
00:13:22,199 --> 00:13:25,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手？你有听我说话吗？</font>

192
00:13:25,339 --> 00:13:30,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 有在听啦 你是在问西瓜是蔬菜还是水果吧？</font>

193
00:13:31,599 --> 00:13:32,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没错</font>

194
00:13:32,889 --> 00:13:38,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">跑到蔬果店买西瓜 结果端出来一个蜜瓜 真是吓死我了</font>

195
00:13:38,489 --> 00:13:41,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉从刚才开始就前言不搭后语的</font>

196
00:13:41,649 --> 00:13:45,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还都是在说一些无聊的事情</font>

197
00:13:45,529 --> 00:13:51,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">-没想到那个完美无缺 冷静沉着 史上最强大侦探 -而蜜瓜呢 它就是蜜瓜啦</font>

198
00:13:51,069 --> 00:13:53,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">-会一直翻来覆去地说闲话 -而蜜瓜呢 它就是蜜瓜啦</font>

199
00:13:53,059 --> 00:13:54,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">会一直翻来覆去地说闲话</font>

200
00:13:54,619 --> 00:13:58,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">肯定是在谈论什么高雅的话题吧</font>

201
00:13:58,689 --> 00:13:59,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂</font>

202
00:14:00,309 --> 00:14:03,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么一直都离这么远啊</font>

203
00:14:07,699 --> 00:14:09,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">过来啊</font>

204
00:14:11,079 --> 00:14:12,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要我坐床上？</font>

205
00:14:12,599 --> 00:14:15,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 坐到这里聊天嘛</font>

206
00:14:16,109 --> 00:14:21,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这可不大好吧 孤男寡女坐在一张床上…</font>

207
00:14:22,159 --> 00:14:23,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不行吗？</font>

208
00:14:25,729 --> 00:14:27,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 没问题</font>

209
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:34,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这还是我们头一回睡在一起呢</font>

210
00:14:38,509 --> 00:14:40,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就在我身边</font>

211
00:14:43,029 --> 00:14:47,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">嗯 还是那张过两天就会忘掉的脸呢</font>

212
00:14:47,259 --> 00:14:49,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在是说这个的时候？</font>

213
00:14:51,449 --> 00:14:53,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">呵呵 欺负你是件很开心的事哦</font>

214
00:14:54,569 --> 00:14:59,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 其实你也喜欢被我欺负吧</font>

215
00:15:00,329 --> 00:15:02,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要捏造这种古怪的设定</font>

216
00:15:03,789 --> 00:15:07,709
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是不是要我一辈子都不欺负你了？</font>

217
00:15:09,289 --> 00:15:11,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">永远都不和你说话？</font>

218
00:15:16,569 --> 00:15:19,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这人还是这么有意思</font>

219
00:15:20,829 --> 00:15:21,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">烦死了</font>

220
00:15:22,609 --> 00:15:24,809
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">闹别扭的表情也有点可爱</font>

221
00:15:25,589 --> 00:15:27,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这可算不上是夸奖</font>

222
00:15:28,819 --> 00:15:31,749
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是过上两天就会忘记了</font>

223
00:15:34,249 --> 00:15:34,889
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是</font>

224
00:15:36,509 --> 00:15:39,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和你一起度过的这三年</font>

225
00:15:39,989 --> 00:15:41,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是绝对不会忘记的</font>

226
00:15:47,209 --> 00:15:50,059
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么感觉正经起来了呢</font>

227
00:15:50,399 --> 00:15:53,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你这人没了正经还剩什么啊</font>

228
00:15:54,009 --> 00:15:57,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真过分 你把我当什么人了</font>

229
00:15:58,839 --> 00:16:00,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">既然如此 偶尔…</font>

230
00:16:02,679 --> 00:16:05,849
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">也来做些不正经的事？</font>

231
00:16:36,919 --> 00:16:38,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好想死</font>

232
00:16:38,999 --> 00:16:42,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">昨天的我到底在想什么啊</font>

233
00:16:52,789 --> 00:16:54,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">早上好</font>

234
00:17:25,459 --> 00:17:26,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手</font>

235
00:17:27,479 --> 00:17:29,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">把手伸出来一下</font>

236
00:17:29,969 --> 00:17:31,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">冷静点 谢丝塔</font>

237
00:17:31,859 --> 00:17:35,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">先把那粗粗的针筒放下 我们好好说话</font>

238
00:17:35,909 --> 00:17:38,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事 也就疼那么一瞬间</font>

239
00:17:40,359 --> 00:17:44,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这种注射液能够消除最近一段时间的记忆</font>

240
00:17:45,129 --> 00:17:49,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们当初不是在文化节抓到了厕所的花子小姐吗</font>

241
00:17:49,709 --> 00:17:54,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实这里面就含有一些和当初那种药相似的成分</font>

242
00:17:54,929 --> 00:17:59,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">完蛋了 这不就保证了疗效吗</font>

243
00:18:01,329 --> 00:18:04,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来 助手 伸出手</font>

244
00:18:12,369 --> 00:18:15,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好像有人来了哦 不去开门吗</font>

245
00:18:17,549 --> 00:18:19,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要咂嘴啊</font>

246
00:18:20,999 --> 00:18:21,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哪位</font>

247
00:18:23,349 --> 00:18:26,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉刚才好吵啊 你们干什么呢？</font>

248
00:18:31,529 --> 00:18:33,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">任务完成啦</font>

249
00:18:34,999 --> 00:18:39,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你不会真的在那之后找到了蓝宝石之眼吧</font>

250
00:18:40,259 --> 00:18:43,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">比起那还不知道是否存在的神秘镜片</font>

251
00:18:43,769 --> 00:18:47,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">应该先珍惜一下你那双确实存在的眼睛</font>

252
00:18:55,119 --> 00:18:56,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">被发现啦</font>

253
00:18:57,289 --> 00:19:00,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟都一起行动了两周嘛</font>

254
00:19:01,999 --> 00:19:06,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为当时左眼受伤 我的视力变差了许多</font>

255
00:19:07,349 --> 00:19:11,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以时不时会在街上看丢艾丽西亚</font>

256
00:19:12,279 --> 00:19:15,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不好好戴上眼罩 是治不好的哦</font>

257
00:19:15,899 --> 00:19:20,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看来我有些看错了艾丽西亚这个人</font>

258
00:19:21,089 --> 00:19:26,549
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">「坦率表现喜怒哀乐的少女」只是她的表象</font>

259
00:19:27,169 --> 00:19:29,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">她的本质一定是…</font>

260
00:19:32,209 --> 00:19:34,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就是我的答案哦 对吗？</font>

261
00:19:36,389 --> 00:19:41,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是这样的吗？原来这是谢丝塔给她的考验？</font>

262
00:19:43,049 --> 00:19:45,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">如…如我所料</font>

263
00:19:45,499 --> 00:19:46,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也太不会说谎了！</font>

264
00:19:50,379 --> 00:19:53,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我又不擅长脑筋急转弯</font>

265
00:19:53,769 --> 00:19:56,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好久没看到你那种表情了</font>

266
00:19:56,829 --> 00:19:58,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你好烦啊</font>

267
00:20:00,089 --> 00:20:04,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就那么喜欢比你小的女生送的礼物吗？</font>

268
00:20:05,279 --> 00:20:07,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我不是这个意思</font>

269
00:20:08,089 --> 00:20:10,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟人家一片好意送的 所以才戴着…</font>

270
00:20:12,139 --> 00:20:14,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 抱歉 不是这个意思</font>

271
00:20:15,879 --> 00:20:20,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我只是因为没有发现你的眼睛出了问题</font>

272
00:20:20,399 --> 00:20:22,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而对自己感到羞耻罢了</font>

273
00:20:23,869 --> 00:20:27,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">该怎么说呢 原来你也是个正常人啊</font>

274
00:20:27,999 --> 00:20:32,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是个会被琐碎感情左右的正常人 这挺好的</font>

275
00:20:33,179 --> 00:20:34,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是吗</font>

276
00:20:45,519 --> 00:20:46,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔？</font>

277
00:20:47,519 --> 00:20:48,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没事</font>

278
00:20:48,349 --> 00:20:51,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(蓝宝石幻想)</font>

279
00:20:52,999 --> 00:20:54,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">暂时没事…</font>

280
00:20:58,479 --> 00:21:00,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(日本 东京)</font>

281
00:21:01,019 --> 00:21:02,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂 你好</font>

282
00:21:03,129 --> 00:21:04,599
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哟 臭小鬼</font>

283
00:21:04,959 --> 00:21:10,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你还活着啊 听说你把国家议会搞得乱七八糟？</font>

284
00:21:10,559 --> 00:21:14,499
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">风靡小姐 这话上次见面的时候就该说了吧</font>

285
00:21:14,689 --> 00:21:18,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且 究其原因 这可都是因为你丢给我的开膛手杰克事件</font>

286
00:21:18,619 --> 00:21:20,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">才害我受了那么严重的伤</font>

287
00:21:20,259 --> 00:21:22,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">啊？我们什么时候见面的？</font>

288
00:21:23,209 --> 00:21:29,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说什么呢 不就两周前吗？还说什么蓝宝石之眼如何如何</font>

289
00:21:29,749 --> 00:21:34,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不不 我就只是当时在教堂前见了你们一面啊</font>

290
00:21:35,639 --> 00:21:38,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你把谁认错成我了啊？</font>

291
00:21:38,679 --> 00:21:41,819
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是吧 既然如此 那是…</font>

292
00:21:42,479 --> 00:21:47,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对啊 她当时拿着那个本来已经送给我的打火机</font>

293
00:21:49,399 --> 00:21:52,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在吗？君冢？喂？</font>

294
00:21:52,869 --> 00:21:53,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

295
00:21:57,339 --> 00:22:00,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那时候的风靡小姐 难道是…</font>

296
00:22:06,509 --> 00:22:11,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

297
00:22:11,879 --> 00:22:17,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

298
00:22:17,029 --> 00:22:22,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

299
00:22:22,409 --> 00:22:27,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

300
00:22:27,729 --> 00:22:33,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊著 想要见到某人</font>

301
00:22:33,079 --> 00:22:38,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

302
00:22:38,409 --> 00:22:43,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

303
00:22:43,729 --> 00:22:48,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

304
00:22:48,689 --> 00:22:53,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

305
00:22:54,029 --> 00:23:02,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

306
00:23:03,869 --> 00:23:09,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

307
00:23:09,169 --> 00:23:14,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

308
00:23:14,489 --> 00:23:19,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

309
00:23:19,739 --> 00:23:27,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

310
00:23:35,969 --> 00:23:40,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第8集 然后再次踏上旅程)</font>

